  "method": [
    "Heat the oven to 350°F.",
    "Pat clean chicken and carefully sprinkle with salt.",
    "Organize the top of a baking dish or plate with fried potatoes and",
    "vegetables.",
    "Dress with one teaspoon of salt and black pepper. Insert bits of",
    "chicken.",
    "Take a sauce consisting of lemon-garlic. Stir ¼ cup of olive oil with",
    "lime juice, garlic powder, thyme, and nutmeg together in such a small",
    "mixing dish.",
    "Over the chicken and potatoes, mix equally.",
    "On edge, arrange the lemon wedges. Load the chicken stock from one",
    "hand into the saucepan.",
    "Fry up for 45 minutes to one hour in an exposed warm oven, until",
    "meat and vegetables are tender.",
    "Turn off the heat and substitute, if you prefer, Kalamata olives.",
    "Add a little bit of clean parsley to the garnish.",
    "Present with Taztaziki salad and a piece of flatbread, if you",
    "choose."
  ],
